March 8 (Reuters) - Natural Gas Services Group Inc:
* REG-NATURAL GAS SERVICES GROUP REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER 2017 EARNINGS
* Q4 REVENUE ROSE 4.7 PERCENT TO $16.7 MILLION * NATURAL GAS SERVICES GROUP - NET INCOME FOR 3 MONTHS ENDED DEC 31, 2017 INCREASED TO $18.7 MILLION VERSUS NET INCOME OF $1.2 MILLION FOR SAME PERIOD IN 2016
